{"tid":1040952,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"到底賤種蝗螞點解都有人撐？","createTime":"2019-02-28T12:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T13:29:39.000Z","uid":59491,"like":25,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ac786c9872a6d52ad08e1fd2f8cd3d5af31729ce","tid":1040952,"uid":59491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T12:55:33.000Z","msg":"球風：黑哨 茅底 不死身<br />\n<br />\n球員：用錢買球星 當打機咁 就咁將最出名最貴嘅球員放上場<br />\n對青訓同貢獻良多嘅球員就十分絕情 當人地玩具咁 想要就要 唔要就當垃圾掟<br />\n<br />\n比賽表現：近十年間唔中俾巴塞炒三粒以上 贏巴通常都係一兩球差距 炒到巴三球差距已經係08年嘅事 西甲贏得兩三次<br />\n<br />\n都唔知點解一隊咁嘅球隊都有咁多香港人撐 又唔係細個住馬德里"},{"pid":"8e5ff6f2c2ace39f7d3609fd4464ae33446b2096","tid":1040952,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:24:57.000Z","msg":"樓主怨婦"},{"pid":"9b0b7a087e20bfc52e51af332a9fe3ed11e98c1e","tid":1040952,"uid":67225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8e5ff6f2c2ace39f7d3609fd4464ae33446b2096","tid":1040952,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:24:57.000Z","msg":"樓主怨婦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:29:20.000Z","msg":"你先喺"},{"pid":"ffefa8fe8fe1440b0f6b082ce21a213d61abc2c9","tid":1040952,"uid":104499,"like":3,"dislike":12,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"8e5ff6f2c2ace39f7d3609fd4464ae33446b2096","tid":1040952,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:24:57.000Z","msg":"樓主怨婦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-28T13:29:39.000Z","msg":"你不如睇下史上有幾多隊可以歐聯3連冠先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過照你道理應該都會話年年抽好籤 又黑哨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n何必成日比較呢點解巴塞好波 皇馬唔可以好波"}]}